quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Your God is one God, and those who believe not in the Hereafter their heart are given to denial, and they are inflated with pride"
  16,23,"Without a doubt Allah knows what you keep secret and what you disclose. Verily, He loves not those inflated with pride"
  16,24,"And when it is said to them, \"What is it that your Lord has revealed (sent down)?\" they say, \"Old folks´ tales"
  16,25,"Let them bear the burden of their sins in full on the Day of Resurrection, and also some of the burdens of those whom they led astray without knowledge. Alas! How grievous is the burden they shall bear"